findings: Observed a 4.03% improvement in average F-1 score for the With-AI group
Observed a 24.65% reduction in average effort (as measured by % emails read) for the With-AI group​
Average preference Likert score of 3.67 (on 1-7 scale), slightly favor to No-AI. Median score 4.0 (on 1-7 scale), indifferent between both groups.​
